data.description: Single-owner 'Fenton' floor-plan by Richmond American offering 1,708 SqFt in a comfortable 3-bed, 2-bath home. The covered entrance opens to a private guest bedroom/bathroom corner of the home. A central dining room could double as a home office or playroom for the kiddos. And the spacious kitchen, with walk-in pantry, is open to both a dining nook and sizeable great room, ideal for entertaining (elect in floor for easy island addition). A large master bedroom, with rustic barn door, opens to a roomy master bath and walk-in closet. Out back an extended paver patio enlarges the outdoor living space to enjoy summer BBQ's (w/natural gas pre-plumb), perimeter planter boxes and sunset mountain views! A corner lot means just one neighbor and all just a stone's throw from the neighborhood park.
